<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f4f4; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #18181b; padding: 28px 32px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
    .body { padding: 32px; }
    .highlight { background: #f9f9fb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .highlight strong { display: block; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .highlight span { color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    .fact-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 14px; }
    .fact-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 32px; background: #f9f9fb; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>SpeakFlow</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>안녕하세요, <strong><%= @user.name %></strong>님!</p>
      <p><strong><%= @plan.name %></strong> 멤버십에 가입해 주셔서 감사합니다. 지금 바로 강의를 시작해 보세요.</p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong><%= @plan.name %></strong>
        <span>월 <%= number_to_currency(@plan.monthly_price, unit: "원", precision: 0, format: "%n%u") %></span>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span>시작일</span>
          <strong><%= @subscription.started_at.strftime("%Y.%m.%d") %></strong>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span>다음 결제일</span>
          <strong><%= @subscription.current_period_end.strftime("%Y.%m.%d") %></strong>
        </div>
        <% if @plan.monthly_coaching_credits.positive? %>
        <div class="fact-row">
          <span>포함 첨삭 크레딧</span>
          <strong>월 <%= @plan.monthly_coaching_credits %>회</strong>
        </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 28px;">
        <a href="<%= root_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #18181b; color: #fff; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">SpeakFlow 시작하기</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>SpeakFlow · 이 메일은 자동으로 발송되었습니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
